# Release History

## 1.1.0-beta.1 (2026-01-12)

- Azure Resource Manager Purview client library for Java. This package contains Microsoft Azure SDK for Purview Management SDK. Creates a Microsoft.Purview management client. Package api-version 2024-04-01-preview. For documentation on how to use this package, please see [Azure Management Libraries for Java](https://aka.ms/azsdk/java/mgmt).
